Monday June 5 Iris receives shocking news. Mkabayi and the UTA make a smart move against the Ngwenyas while Samson makes interesting changes to his lifestyle. Tuesday June 6 Iris threatens the livelihood of the Ngwenyas. Lerato worries about her safety while Samson avoids spending time with Khanyi. Wednesday June 7 Judas makes Iris an offer. Blade makes a gruesome discovery. Mandla interrupts a moment between Samson and Mabuyi and later, Khanyi s little crusade yields positive results for Sihle. Thursday June 8 Judas worries about the threat to his wealth. Mkabayi has an explosive encounter with Lillian. Samson lies about why he can t go away with Khanyi. Meanwhile, the wives grow suspicious of Mpiyakhe s actions. Friday June 9 Tension between Lillian and Judas escalates, resulting in a dark secret being revealed. Iris is forced to make a deal with the devil. Meanwhile, Samson is desperate for some alone time with Mabuyi.